                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-robot fs-1 text-white mb-3"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="display-6 text-white fw-bold mb-3">Meet BloomBot</h2>
                    <p class="lead text-white mb-4 opacity-90">
                        AI-powered assistant trained on NASA Earth observation data, ready to answer your questions about flowering events,
                        climate impacts, and conservation strategies.
                    </p>
                    <button class="btn btn-light btn-lg px-5 py-3 rounded-pill shadow" onclick="toggleChatbot()">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-comments me-2"></i>
